  <entry>
    <title>Ubuntu18 基础配置</title>
    <url>/2021/12/12/Ubuntu18-%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Ubuntu18-安装虚拟环境"><a href="#Ubuntu18-安装虚拟环境" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu18 安装虚拟环境"></a>Ubuntu18 安装虚拟环境</h2><p><strong>通过apt安装virtualenv</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install virtualenv</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install virtualenvwrapper</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>在.bashrc 中添加 下面两行，根据自己的目录进行路径修改</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> WORKON_HOME=<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.virtualenvs</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> /usr/share/virtualenvwrapper/virtualenvwrapper.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>保存后在终端执行以下命令</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> .bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>创建指定版本python的虚拟环境</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkvirtualenv venv --python=/usr/bin/python3.6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Ubuntu18-安装OneNote"><a href="#Ubuntu18-安装OneNote" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu18 安装OneNote"></a>Ubuntu18 安装OneNote</h2><p><strong>只需要两行命令</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install snap</span><br><span class="line">sudo snap install p3x-onenote</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Ubuntu18-安装截图软件"><a href="#Ubuntu18-安装截图软件" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu18 安装截图软件"></a>Ubuntu18 安装截图软件</h2><h3 id="Ubuntu18-安装flameshot"><a href="#Ubuntu18-安装flameshot" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu18 安装flameshot"></a>Ubuntu18 安装flameshot</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install flameshot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>配置快捷键：<br>设置&gt;设备&gt;键盘，设置一个自定义的快捷键（拉倒最下边）<br>名称：截图<br>命令填写：flameshot gui<br>截完图后保存：Ctrl + S<br>复制到粘贴板：Ctrl + C</p>
<h2 id="Ubuntu18-安装WPS办公软件"><a href="#Ubuntu18-安装WPS办公软件" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu18 安装WPS办公软件"></a>Ubuntu18 安装WPS办公软件</h2><h3 id="卸载原生liboffice"><a href="#卸载原生liboffice" class="headerlink" title="卸载原生liboffice"></a>卸载原生liboffice</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get remove libreoffice-common</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>以后安装回来使用：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install libreoffice</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="官网下载WPS并安装"><a href="#官网下载WPS并安装" class="headerlink" title="官网下载WPS并安装"></a>官网下载WPS并安装</h3><p><strong>下载wps deb包(<a href="https://www.wps.cn/product/wpslinux/">https://www.wps.cn/product/wpslinux/</a>)</strong><br><strong>安装</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i wps……</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="第一次打开wps-文档提示缺少字体"><a href="#第一次打开wps-文档提示缺少字体" class="headerlink" title="第一次打开wps 文档提示缺少字体"></a>第一次打开wps 文档提示缺少字体</h3><h4 id="下载字体https-pan-baidu-com-s-1mh0lcbY"><a href="#下载字体https-pan-baidu-com-s-1mh0lcbY" class="headerlink" title="下载字体https://pan.baidu.com/s/1mh0lcbY"></a>下载字体<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1mh0lcbY">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1mh0lcbY</a></h4><h4 id="解压缩"><a href="#解压缩" class="headerlink" title="解压缩"></a>解压缩</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unzip wps_symbol_fonts.zip</span><br><span class="line">sudo mv  wps_symbol_fonts  /usr/share/fonts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="修改字体权限，终端执行以下命令"><a href="#修改字体权限，终端执行以下命令" class="headerlink" title="修改字体权限，终端执行以下命令"></a>修改字体权限，终端执行以下命令</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /usr/share/fonts/</span><br><span class="line">chmod 755 wps_symbol_fonts</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /usr/share/fonts/wps_symbol_fonts</span><br><span class="line">chmod 644 *</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="生成字体索引-终端执行以下命令"><a href="#生成字体索引-终端执行以下命令" class="headerlink" title="生成字体索引,终端执行以下命令"></a>生成字体索引,终端执行以下命令</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /usr/share/fonts/wps_symbol_fonts</span><br><span class="line">sudo mkfontscale</span><br><span class="line">sudo mkfontdir</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="更新字体缓存-终端执行以下命令"><a href="#更新字体缓存-终端执行以下命令" class="headerlink" title="更新字体缓存,终端执行以下命令"></a>更新字体缓存,终端执行以下命令</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo fc-cache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="重启WPS"><a href="#重启WPS" class="headerlink" title="重启WPS"></a>重启WPS</h4><h3 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h3><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_25135655/article/details/104394488">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_25135655/article/details/104394488</a></p>
]]></content>
